# Greg CRM — MVP Implementation Plan

A local-first, agent-native CRM where contacts are markdown files. Built for founders, consultants and startup operators who hate Salesforce.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **v1 wedge:** Warm intros & follow-ups for founders. Not a full sales CRM. Narrow and opinionated.

## Architecture

| Layer | Choice | Why |
|-------|--------|-----|
| **Frontend** | Vite + React | Browser-first MVP, fast iteration |
| **Styling** | Vanilla CSS (Linear/Notion-inspired) | Clean, spacious, premium feel |
| **Markdown** | `gray-matter` + `react-markdown` | Parse YAML frontmatter + render body |
| **Storage** | localStorage (MVP) → filesystem (Electron, Phase 2) | Ship fast, add Electron later |
| **Command Palette** | Custom component | Cmd+K primary interface |
| **Fonts** | Inter + JetBrains Mono | Modern, readable |

### Contact File Format (`~/greg/contacts/john-doe.md`)

```markdown
---
name: John Doe
email: john@example.com
company: Acme Corp
role: CTO
tags: [investor, technical]
phone: "+1-555-0123"
linkedin: https://linkedin.com/in/johndoe
status: warm
last_contacted: 2026-03-01
created: 2026-02-15
---

## Notes
Met at YC Demo Day. Interested in our Series A.

## Activity
- **2026-03-01** — Sent follow-up email about partnership
- **2026-02-20** — Coffee meeting, discussed roadmap
- **2026-02-15** — Initial intro via Sarah
```

## Proposed Changes

### Design System

#### [NEW] `src/index.css`
Dark-mode-first, Linear/Notion-inspired design system:
- Spacious layout, subtle borders, clean typography
- Soft gradients, glassmorphism accents
- Smooth micro-animations
- Premium feel — not a dev tool, a **founder tool**

---

### App Shell & Components

#### [NEW] `src/App.jsx`
Three-panel layout: sidebar → contact list → detail view. Hosts Cmd+K overlay.

#### [NEW] `src/components/Sidebar.jsx`
Navigation rail with contact groups, tags, search. Collapsible.

#### [NEW] `src/components/ContactList.jsx`
Scrollable contact cards with avatar, name, company, last-contacted indicator.

#### [NEW] `src/components/ContactDetail.jsx`
Full contact view: header with key info, tags, rendered notes, activity timeline. Toggle to edit mode.

#### [NEW] `src/components/CommandPalette.jsx`
Cmd+K overlay with fuzzy search. Initial commands:
- "New contact" / "Search contacts" / "Add tag"
- "Show people I haven't talked to in 30 days"
- "Draft follow-up to [contact]"

#### [NEW] `src/components/ContactEditor.jsx`
Create/edit form: frontmatter fields as clean inputs + markdown body editor.

#### [NEW] `src/components/EmptyState.jsx`
Beautiful welcome state when no contacts exist yet.

---

### Data Layer

#### [NEW] `src/lib/contacts.js`
CRUD operations on contacts (localStorage for MVP):
- `listContacts()`, `getContact(id)`, `saveContact(data)`, `deleteContact(id)`
- `searchContacts(query)`, `filterByTag(tag)`

#### [NEW] `src/lib/markdown.js`
Parse/serialize markdown with YAML frontmatter using `gray-matter`.

#### [NEW] `src/hooks/useContacts.js`
React state management for contacts list + selected contact.

#### [NEW] `src/hooks/useCommandPalette.js`
Command palette state, fuzzy search, command registry.

---

### Sample Data

#### [NEW] `src/data/sampleContacts.js`
4-5 realistic sample contacts for first-run experience (VC, co-founder, advisor, customer, press).

